  - m_Id: 642065645568
    m_Localized: AnatomiQ
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 667670027976704
    m_Localized: Your device is getting warm, so some visual detail has been reduced
      to keep things running smoothly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 667670057336832
    m_Localized: "Your device is hot. AnatomiQ is briefly easing off to let it cool
      down \u2014 this will pass in a moment."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
